T02TD3110E:205a-1: a'arya ta th'a ga toshn'i sha si t'a ta pa tre n'a ma aa ba r'a dzi ta au pa de sha / bod skad du /
T02TD3110E:205a-2: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor nas byung ba'i gdugs dkar mo can gzhan gyis mi thub pa zhes bya ba'i nye bar bshad pa /
T02TD3110E:205a-3: bcom ldan 'das gdugs dkar mo can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3110E:205a-4: snying rje chen pos sems bskyed de /
T02TD3110E:205b-0: mandal legs par byugs te thig la dang me tog gi tshom bu bkram @205b nas spyan drangs pa dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-1: mchod pa sngon du 'gro bas legs pa dang ldan pa la mchod pa dang gtor ma sbyin par bya'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-2: de nas mandal la aa las zla ba la aom bsams la /
T02TD3110E:205b-4: bsdu ba byas pa las bcom ldan 'das ma gdugs dkar mo zhal gsum ma /
T02TD3110E:205b-5: zhal gsum la spyan gsum gsum yod pa'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-6: sngo ba dang dmar ba ni g-yon dang g-yas kyi zhal la'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-7: rgyan sna tshogs pas brgyan pa phyag brgyad pa /
T02TD3110E:205b-8: g-yas kyi dang po na gdugs dkar po /
T02TD3110E:205b-12: g-yon dang po na rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-13: gnyis pan rdo rje dkar po'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-15: bzhi pa na zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub ni g-yon pa'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-16: khros pa'i stangs dang bcas pas ma rungs pa thams cad 'jigs par byed pa'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-17: 'od zer lcags kyu dang 'dra bas ye shes kyi lha dgug pa dang gzhug pa dang bcing ba dang dbang du bya'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-18: dbang du bskur ba la bee ro tsa na'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-19: phyag dang mchod pa byas nas sngon du byas te dmigs pa bcu bzhis bklag par bya'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-20: legs pa dang ldan pa la gzungs kyis bstod pa bya'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-21: yang na mdun du dmigs te bstan pa ltar kun yid kyis bya ba yin no //
T02TD3110E:205b-22: dmigs pa bcu bzhi ni phyag gi dmigs pa dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-24: ri khrod lo ma can nyi shu rtsa gnyis dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-26: bcom ldan 'das ma'i che ba dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-28: gdon chen po nyi shu rtsa bzhi bzlog pa dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-31: dam tshig can bcu bzhi'i sngags dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-33: nad thams cad bsrung ba dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-36: 'di dang phyi mar phun sum tshogs pa dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-37: bu sri dang g-yul zhi ba dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-38: khyad par du bdag bsrung ba dang /
T02TD3110E:205b-40: / gshegs pa dang bsdu ba byas te/ m ji ltar bde bar gnas par bya'o //
T02TD3110E:205b-41: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor nas byung a'i gdugs dkar mo can gzhan gyis mi thub pa zhes bya ba'i nye bar bshad pa bla ma rdo rje gad na pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3110E:205b-43: // / pandi ta chen po de nyid dang /
T02TD3110E:206a-0: @206a * // lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o//
